18:12.508 --> 18:14.676
<i>for the upcoming Republican
National Convention</i>

18:14.676 --> 18:15.886
<i>in San Diego.</i>

18:15.886 --> 18:19.348
<i>Anderson quotes ITT's
top lobbyist, Dita Beard,</i>

18:19.348 --> 18:21.642
<i>saying she discussed
arrangements for settling</i>

18:21.642 --> 18:23.727
<i>the case with Attorney General
