18:23.727 --> 18:25.646
<i>at a party last May.</i>

18:29.691 --> 18:32.152
- Liddy here.
- It's Howard. Got your message.

18:32.152 --> 18:35.447
<i>Howard, thank you
for, uh, calling me back.</i>

18:35.447 --> 18:37.491
<i>Of course.
I just read the paper.</i>

18:37.491 --> 18:39.076
You saw it?
<i>Hmm.</i>

18:39.076 --> 18:42.162
"We now have evidence
that the settlement

18:42.162 --> 18:46.375
of the Nixon Administration's
biggest antitrust case

18:46.375 --> 18:50.504
was privately arranged between
Attorney General John Mitchell

18:50.504 --> 18:53.382
and the top lobbyist
for the company involved."

18:53.382 --> 18:56.218
<i>"For 400,000 dollars
in hotel rooms,</i>

18:56.218 --> 19:00.848
and we have this on the word
of the lobbyist herself,

19:00.848 --> 19:03.141
crusty, capable Dita Beard,

19:03.141 --> 19:05.561
the International Telephone
and Telegraph Company.

19:05.561 --> 19:08.772
She acknowledged the secret deal
after we obtained

19:08.772 --> 19:11.942
a highly incriminating memo,

19:11.942 --> 19:15.028
written by her,
from ITT's files."

19:15.028 --> 19:16.822
<i>They're going
to crucify Mitchell.</i>

19:16.822 --> 19:20.534
<i>And the president,
unless we can figure out
how to stop it.</i>

19:20.534 --> 19:22.369
Shit.

19:22.369 --> 19:23.829
<i>We've got
a second chance, Howard.</i>

19:23.829 --> 19:25.539
<i>I will call you later.</i>

19:27.082 --> 19:28.709
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

