Hey, Gordo.

19:30.127 --> 19:33.088
You see the papers? Dita Beard?

19:33.088 --> 19:36.758
Jack Anderson has her memo
that says Mitchell got Justice

19:36.758 --> 19:38.760
to drop an antitrust lawsuit

19:38.760 --> 19:41.597
