of felony bribery.

19:51.607 --> 19:53.734
If they connect this
to the president...

19:53.734 --> 19:54.776
Calm down, okay.

19:54.776 --> 19:56.361
The White House said
that the memo's a fake.

19:56.361 --> 19:58.530
It's just the usual anti-Nixon
hatchet job

19:58.530 --> 20:02.910
by the liberal press.
This will blow over, trust me.

20:02.910 --> 20:06.371
- ♪ (DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
