20:17.716 --> 20:19.092
<i>raised by the so-called</i>

20:19.092 --> 20:20.969
<i>- Dita Beard memo.</i>
- ♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

20:20.969 --> 20:23.305
Well,
Mitchell's officially fucked.

20:23.305 --> 20:25.849
But we still need
to have a goddamned convention.

20:25.849 --> 20:28.018
Yeah, well, I'm not going
to hang him out to dry.

20:28.018 --> 20:29.770
Jim, we are moving
the convention to Miami,

20:29.770 --> 20:31.230
ergo, we're not paying

20:31.230 --> 20:33.440
a San Diego security firm
jack shit.

20:33.440 --> 20:34.775
All right, I'm gonna call him
right now.

20:34.775 --> 20:36.443
Okay, I'll have the president
send him a bunch

20:36.443 --> 20:37.778
of fucking buttons or something.

20:40.322 --> 20:41.907
Oh, may I see some ID?

20:45.827 --> 20:48.872
<i>...in which
she emphatically denied...</i>
- Jeb.

20:48.872 --> 20:53.001
Howard and I would like to talk
to the attorney general
and offer our support.

20:53.001 --> 20:55.170
Are you two
out of your fucking minds?

20:55.170 --> 20:57.381
Do you think John Mitchell
gives a rat's ass

20:57.381 --> 20:59.174
about your bullshit pranks
right now?

20:59.174 --> 21:01.677
Mitchell doesn't want to hear
from you two bozos.

21:01.677 --> 21:05.013
The almighty United States
Senate is investigating

21:05.013 --> 21:07.015
this ITT memo bullshit. Okay?

21:07.015 --> 21:09.518
We had to move the entire
convention out of San Diego

21:09.518 --> 21:12.437
so there would be no reminder
of Sheraton Hotels.

21:13.021 --> 21:14.064
And the worst part,

21:14.064 --> 21:17.067
is that we had 400 grand
in free hotel rooms.

21:17.067 --> 21:19.903
And you know who's paying
for it now? I am!

21:21.863 --> 21:24.366
<i>Columnist Jack Anderson returned
for a final day of testimony...</i>

21:24.366 --> 21:26.201
I knew this Dita Beard stuff
was gonna come back

21:26.201 --> 21:27.411
and bite us in the ass.

21:27.411 --> 21:31.289
- This is the whole reelection!
- What can I do to help?

21:31.289 --> 21:34.126
You want to help?
Go kill Jack Anderson.

21:35.252 --> 21:39.756
- Roger that.
- I mean...

21:39.756 --> 21:43.135
<i>...and for him
to suggest that he didn't know</i>

21:43.135 --> 21:44.219
<i>about the arrangements</i>

21:44.219 --> 21:46.304
<i>for the convention
that he's going to direct,</i>

21:46.304 --> 21:49.391
<i>uh...
...that strains the truth.</i>

21:49.391 --> 21:51.560
<i>- And, uh...</i>
- I just talked to my guy.

21:51.560 --> 21:53.645
If we don't pay,
he's going to sue.

21:53.645 --> 21:54.980
Uh, where is Gordon?

21:54.980 --> 21:57.065
- He left.
- Where'd he go?

21:57.065 --> 21:58.692
He said he was off
to kill Jack Anderson.

21:58.692 --> 22:01.111
- ♪ (DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
- Oh, shit. Here.

22:04.031 --> 22:06.241
Move! Goddammit, move! Move!

22:06.241 --> 22:10.662
Gordon! Gordon! Hey! Hey!

22:12.414 --> 22:14.916
- ♪ (TENSE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪
- McCord told me--

22:14.916 --> 22:17.919
Are you going
to shoot Jack Anderson?

22:21.131 --> 22:25.552
When I get an order,
I execute it, Jeb.

22:25.552 --> 22:27.929
I was joking, you crazy bastard!

22:27.929 --> 22:31.308
Come on,
I want to talk to you upstairs.

22:34.102 --> 22:36.980
I am no joke.

22:38.273 --> 22:41.234
I am serious. Deadly serious.

22:43.445 --> 22:46.990
You touch me again,
and I will kill you.

22:55.332 --> 22:57.751
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

22:57.751 --> 23:01.713
Yes, if you could
have, uh, Dr. Downey call back

23:01.713 --> 23:03.131
as soon as possible.

23:04.132 --> 23:06.968
Well, it's about
my daughter, Lisa.

23:06.968 --> 23:07.969
Howard.

23:07.969 --> 23:09.554
Yeah. Okay. Thank you.

23:09.554 --> 23:11.473
I left word with the doctor.

23:11.473 --> 23:13.266
- She's going to be okay.
- She-- she's locked herself

23:13.266 --> 23:14.476
in the bathroom.

23:14.476 --> 23:17.062
She won't come out.
It's-- It's getting worse.

23:17.062 --> 23:18.772
♪ (TENSE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

23:20.774 --> 23:24.778
Lisa. Open up.
Your mother's getting worried.

23:24.778 --> 23:26.363
Maybe she fell asleep?

23:26.363 --> 23:28.073
- In the tub?
- I hear something.

23:28.073 --> 23:29.616
Lisa? Sweetie?

23:29.616 --> 23:33.453
- Lisa, open this door right now!
- Don't yell.

23:33.453 --> 23:36.248
- I'm not yelling!
- Yelling doesn't help anything.

23:36.248 --> 23:38.166
- Is Lisa gonna be okay?
- Go back in your room!

23:38.166 --> 23:41.628
Don't yell at him!
Lisa, open this door right now,

23:41.628 --> 23:44.005
or I'm gonna break it down!
Howard. Howard!

23:44.005 --> 23:45.841
Go answer that.

23:45.841 --> 23:47.592
It might be the doctor.

23:49.344 --> 23:52.722
What a nightmare.
Lisa, please. Lisa.

23:58.937 --> 24:01.356
- ♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪
- Hunt residence.

24:01.356 --> 24:03.191
- COLSON'S SECRETARY:
<i>Howard Hunt, please?</i>
- Speaking.

24:03.191 --> 24:05.485
COLSON'S SECRETARY:
<i>I have Charles Colson calling
from the White House.</i>

24:05.485 --> 24:07.654
- Put him through.
- COLSON'S SECRETARY:
<i>Hold, please.</i>

24:09.531 --> 24:11.658
<i>Howard!</i>
- Mm.

24:11.658 --> 24:13.827
Chuck!
How the hell are you?

24:13.827 --> 24:16.955
<i>Doing good, and you?</i>
- Oh, fine and dandy.

24:16.955 --> 24:21.877
Just a typical
Saturday with the family.

24:21.877 --> 24:23.378
<i>Howard,
there's been a development</i>

24:23.378 --> 24:24.963
<i>with the Dita Beard situation.</i>

24:24.963 --> 24:26.381
Sweetie? Lisa.

24:27.132 --> 24:29.259
Sis? Come on. Open up. Please?

24:29.259 --> 24:31.303
What did the doctor say?

24:31.303 --> 24:33.847
That was Colson.
I'm needed at the White House.

24:33.847 --> 24:35.599
No. You're needed here.

24:35.599 --> 24:37.142
Your family needs you.

24:37.142 --> 24:39.394
Your daughter needs you.
I need you!

24:39.394 --> 24:42.856
I don't know
what to do with this.

24:42.856 --> 24:46.651
She won't come out.
Everything I do is wrong.

24:46.651 --> 24:47.861
What do you want from me?

24:47.861 --> 24:50.280
How about for once
you make us feel like we matter

24:50.280 --> 24:54.117
more than your stupid job
or the stupid White House?

24:54.117 --> 24:56.286
That you give a damn
about your family?

24:57.412 --> 25:00.665
Lisa. Lisa, please, honey.
Come on.

25:02.626 --> 25:04.294
Sweetie?

25:10.550 --> 25:12.761
What the fuck!
Lisa?

25:12.761 --> 25:15.931
She's fine. I care.
I'm going to work.

25:17.057 --> 25:18.850
- Honey.
- Hi, Mama.

25:18.850 --> 25:20.644
- My God.
- ♪ (TENSE MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

25:28.735 --> 25:29.778
Sorry.

25:31.821 --> 25:35.283
Gentlemen. The White House's
experts say the Dita Beard memo

25:35.283 --> 25:36.326
is a problem.

25:36.326 --> 25:38.995
But if we can keep
Beard from testifying,

25:38.995 --> 25:41.373
the case against Mitchell
will collapse.

25:41.373 --> 25:43.833
Uh, I'm sorry. Sorry.
So what do you need us for?

25:43.833 --> 25:48.672
Because the Senate
deposes Beard tomorrow...

25:48.672 --> 25:51.800
and if she testifies
that she did write it,

25:51.800 --> 25:54.094
her testimony will be
on the record, then the...

25:55.887 --> 25:58.098
that's enough
for the Senate to keep digging.

25:58.098 --> 25:59.724
And why would she do that?

25:59.724 --> 26:02.227
- Jesus Christ.
- That's why Colson wants us

26:02.227 --> 26:04.896
to get her out of town
and shut her up.

26:04.896 --> 26:08.024
That would certainly
be fortunate.

26:08.024 --> 26:11.361
Gentlemen. Who knows? You may
even impress Mr. Mitchell.

26:14.531 --> 26:16.950
You know what we could do
which would solve this problem--

26:16.950 --> 26:20.495
Please, Gordon,
do not say, "Kill her."

26:22.789 --> 26:27.335
A dead dog chases no cars.

26:27.335 --> 26:32.882
The murder
of the Senate's lead witness

26:32.882 --> 26:37.345
would not lessen Mitchell's
legal scrutiny.

26:37.345 --> 26:41.016
Fine. But solving this
would put us

26:41.016 --> 26:43.184
in Mitchell's good graces.

26:43.184 --> 26:47.230
Yeah. That is going
to take some finesse.

26:47.230 --> 26:48.773
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

27:11.463 --> 27:14.090
♪ (SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

27:22.098 --> 27:23.475
Who the fuck are you?

27:23.475 --> 27:26.811
Mrs. Beard,
my name is George F. Leonard,

27:26.811 --> 27:28.104
and I am an attorney.

27:28.104 --> 27:32.359
Bullshit! You look like one
of those Manson family freaks.

27:32.359 --> 27:36.821
I apologize for the late hour
and the disguise,

27:36.821 --> 27:40.742
but I suspect
you are under FBI surveillance.

27:45.830 --> 27:46.873
What do you want?

27:46.873 --> 27:50.251
I'm here to offer you
some free legal advice.

28:00.512 --> 28:03.139
Hmm. How many kids do you have?

28:03.139 --> 28:04.432
Five.
- Oh?

28:04.432 --> 28:07.602
All grown or in military school.

28:07.602 --> 28:10.438
Outstanding. I have five myself.

28:11.272 --> 28:12.565
So, George,

28:12.565 --> 28:16.194
you said you had friends
at the White House?

28:16.194 --> 28:18.988
Affirmative.

28:18.988 --> 28:23.201
Well, some fair-haired fucker
over there is spreading rumors

28:23.201 --> 28:26.121
that Jack Anderson
and I are homosexuals,

28:26.121 --> 28:30.917
that we're in cahoots
on some sort of lesbo-homo plot

28:30.917 --> 28:33.461
against Nixon.

28:33.461 --> 28:36.381
I can assure you,
I know nothing about that.

28:36.381 --> 28:37.966
Neither homo nor lesbo.

28:37.966 --> 28:40.343
Do I look like a lesbian?

28:40.343 --> 28:42.804
No, ma'am.
You seem straight as I am.

28:42.804 --> 28:46.307
They're making me a pariah!
My own party!

28:46.307 --> 28:48.476
I am in some goddamn pickle!

28:48.476 --> 28:52.188
You're not wrong.
You could go to jail.

28:52.188 --> 28:56.401
Thanks for the pick-me-up,
fella. Shit on a shingle.

28:56.401 --> 29:01.948
But... here's the good news,
you can avoid being deposed,

29:01.948 --> 29:05.743
with no legal repercussions.
Just abracadabra,

29:05.743 --> 29:10.540
- it all goes away.
- But I did write the memo.

29:10.540 --> 29:14.419
And I told Anderson
I wrote the memo.

29:14.419 --> 29:17.046
They're grilling me first thing
in the morning.

29:18.923 --> 29:22.969
Do you have any,
um, medical conditions?

29:22.969 --> 29:25.889
I'm a very physical woman, George.

29:25.889 --> 29:31.978
Hiking, camping,
snowmobiling... fucking.

29:34.397 --> 29:38.109
I meant, like...
cancer in the family?

29:38.943 --> 29:40.820
- I wish.
- Psychiatric problems?

29:40.820 --> 29:43.781
- Oh, hell no.
- Fainting spells?

29:43.781 --> 29:46.326
George,
I am as healthy as a horse,

29:46.326 --> 29:48.536
except for the occasional angina.

29:53.958 --> 29:55.627
What is angina?

29:55.627 --> 29:56.878
<i>Coming through!</i>

29:56.878 --> 29:59.422
Rocky Mountain is the finest
osteopathic hospital

29:59.422 --> 30:01.508
in the greater Denver
Metropolitan Area.

30:01.508 --> 30:04.135
Osteopath? You may as well
take her to a veterinarian.

30:04.135 --> 30:06.346
And you're on oxygen!
Why are you...

30:06.346 --> 30:08.389
Edwina, you are raising
my blood pressure!

30:10.517 --> 30:14.312
Hold the door!
Hold the door!

30:14.312 --> 30:16.481
<i>Dita Beard
experienced chest pains</i>

30:16.481 --> 30:17.649
<i>while flying into Denver</i>

30:17.649 --> 30:19.984
<i>and had to receive
oxygen on the flight.</i>

30:19.984 --> 30:23.154
<i>Mrs. Beard was admitted
to an area hospital</i>

30:23.154 --> 30:24.614
<i>in a serious condition.</i>

30:24.614 --> 30:26.783
As for Dita Beard
getting out of bed

30:26.783 --> 30:29.202
to come back to Washington,
not now,

30:29.202 --> 30:32.413
and not for some time yet,
doctor's orders.

30:38.044 --> 30:39.921
<i>We've got a problem, Howard.</i>

30:39.921 --> 30:41.673
<i>- A Dita Beard problem.</i>
- ♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

30:41.673 --> 30:43.675
A team of senators
is heading to Colorado

30:43.675 --> 30:45.385
to depose her in two days,

30:45.385 --> 30:47.679
including your good friend,
Teddy Kennedy.

30:47.679 --> 30:49.597
That fat-headed booze bag.

30:49.597 --> 30:51.849
They should depose him
about Chappaquiddick.

30:51.849 --> 30:53.601
If there were any justice
in the world.

30:53.601 --> 30:55.353
You know, it wouldn't be
the worst thing for Beard

30:55.353 --> 30:58.398
to actually have a heart attack,
right as Kennedy's grilling her.

30:58.398 --> 30:59.482
Then you could say,

30:59.482 --> 31:01.734
"Senator, now,
you've killed two women!"

31:03.736 --> 31:06.906
Howard, this Beard thing
keeps escalating.

31:06.906 --> 31:11.202
I know. What if Beard herself
were to question

31:11.202 --> 31:13.871
the memo's authenticity?

31:13.871 --> 31:15.832
Hypothetically,
how much in the way

31:15.832 --> 31:18.793
of funds could someone
access for the purposes

31:18.793 --> 31:21.546
- of such an endeavor?
- No. No, no, no.

31:21.546 --> 31:24.465
There is no way I or anyone
at the committee would authorize

31:24.465 --> 31:28.386
funds to influence the testimony
of a witness in a federal case.

31:28.386 --> 31:30.805
What about ITT?

31:30.805 --> 31:32.348
She's still on the payroll.

31:35.560 --> 31:38.187
Say no more. I know what to do.

31:39.397 --> 31:41.691
I feel the need
to say this again, Howard.

31:41.691 --> 31:42.942
For the record,

31:42.942 --> 31:46.112
I am not even suggesting
that you do anything.

31:48.698 --> 31:49.782
Roger that.

31:49.782 --> 31:52.577
♪ (SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

32:02.587 --> 32:04.047
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

32:04.047 --> 32:06.841
Aw, I don't want
to read this shit.

32:07.759 --> 32:09.761
I want something
with small words

32:09.761 --> 32:12.680
and big pictures. <i>Cosmo.</i>

32:12.680 --> 32:15.183
Okay.

32:15.183 --> 32:17.685
It better be the red
fucking Jell-O this time!

